data.description: Welcome home to this custom open concept, 4 bedroom home with 2 fireplaces and a split floorplan, granite counters, crown molding, amazing master bath, This spacious one acre lot has plenty of parking and even has a 50amp RV hookup. Enjoy beautiful sunsets in the large backyard while cozying up by the 2nd fireplace on the back patio. Only 35 minutes from Fort Worth or Lockheed Martin. Seller is offering 5,000 at closing for carpet allowance or closing costs and this home has an assumable mortgage!! Come see this beautiful home today!
